AC209
  • Ultra Sound Machine Alarm Clock: Featured with alarm clock, white noise, high-quality bluetooth dual speaker, night light, 0-100% dimming screen display, and sleep timer, this multifunctional sound machine keeps you a good company while sleep and casts a private relaxing moment for you.
  • Bluetooth Stereo Dual Speaker: The bluetooth 5.0 technology allows you to play your favorite relaxing music anywhere anytime. Dual 10w speakers will provide you an even better sensuous pleasure. Auto-sync functionality can synchronize the time with daylight saving Time, ensuring that the time on the machine is always accurate.
  • Multiple White Noise Options: 21 natural sounds with 30 adjustable volume levels to create a personalized sleep environment: 5 White Noises-Brown Noise/Pink Noise/White Noise; 3 Fan Sounds; 13 Nature Sounds-Sea Wave/Music Box/Rain/Thunderstorm/Croak/Bird Chirp/Summer Night/Campfire/Wind/Yoga/Meditation. Drift off you to sleep. A boon for those who have trouble sleeping
  • Ambent Night Light: Decorate your room with the built-in nightlight, featuring 7 ambient light options(red, orange, yellow, green, cyan, blue, purple). Easily adjust the brightness from 0-100% for a custom ambiance that suits your preference.
  • Digital Alarm Clock with 8 Wake Up Sounds: 8 different alarm sounds to wake you up gently ( Beep, Piano, Bird Chirp, Sea Wave, Stream, Music Box, Yoga, Meditation )，when alarm goes off, night light comes on so you can Clearly see the buttons ,for snoozing or turning off the alarm !
  • 0-100 Dimming : You can easily slide the slider over the full range to choose your most comfortable display and nightlight brightness, protecting your eyes and sleep quality.

Additional details

Safety Information

This product has a corded electric power source and should be kept out of reach of children. Excessive use of this product may expose you to noise levels that may be harmful to your hearing.

Directions

1. Set up the alarm clock with your desired time and wake-up sound. 2. Choose from 21 white noise, fan, or nature sounds adjust volume to preference. 3. Connect mobile device sound machine via Bluetooth play favorite relaxing music. 4. Adjust night light's brightness color create a soothing ambiance.
